General.Name: Xtek Ltd
General.Description: XTEK Limited provides specialist products and tailored solutions to military, law enforcement, government agencies, space, and commercial sectors. The company offers ballistic armour products comprising soft and hard amour, helmets, shields, carriers, and armour gears; and small unmanned aerial systems and ongoing support services. It also provides portable X-ray equipment, demolition remote firing systems, search and detection equipment, hook and line EOD tools, and heavy RPV robots; and logistics engineering. XTEK Limited was founded in 1978 and is based in Symonston, Australia.
